name: Forstrong Emerging Markets Equity ETF
longDescription: The fund primarily investing, directly or indirectly, in a diversified mix of emerging markets securities. This ETF intends to achieve its investment objective by investing primarily in underlying ETFs that are listed on North American stock exchanges. This fund aims to achieve longterm capital growth.
